        <activityName xml:lang="en">heat production, biomethane, at boiler condensing modulating &lt;100kW</activityName>
        <synonym xml:lang="en">Brennwerttechnik</synonym>
        <includedActivitiesEnd xml:lang="en">The module includes fuel input from low pressure (CH) network, infrastructure (boiler), emissions to air and water, and electricity needed for operation.</includedActivitiesEnd>
        <generalComment>
          <text xml:lang="en" index="0">This dataset is a copy of the global dataset. NOx and CO emissions derived from measurements under controlled conditions; no adjustment to real operation made due to lack of information. Other emission data from different references.</text>
        </generalComment>
      </activity>
